Desert safaris, dhow cruises, theme parks on Yas Island, and cultural tours.


What fun things to do in Abu Dhabi are good for families?

Ferrari World, Warner Bros. World, Yas Waterworld, and SeaWorld Abu Dhabi.


Outdoor activities in Abu Dhabi?

Including kayaking, beach activities, sandboarding, cycling, and hiking trails.


What cultural things to do in Abu Dhabi should I not miss?

Visit Qasr Al Watan, Louvre Abu Dhabi, Sheikh Zayed Mosque, and Al Ain Oasis.


What is the best time of year to enjoy activities in Abu Dhabi?

Between November and April when the weather is cooler and ideal for outdoor activities.


